Karen Sharpe is the mother of North Charleston Police Officer Michael Slager  . 
  She defended her son in an interview and said she will never watch the video footage of the fatal shooting of Walter Scott . 
  Ms Sharpe said she also expressed sympathy for the Scott family . 
  She said she has not watched the video of the shooting or read any news coverage of the incident . 
  Said she cannot believe her son would do anything like this . 
  Also revealed that his wife is eight months pregnant . 
  Slager was caught on video shooting Scott in the back as he ran away . 
  He has been charged with murder and has been fired from his job . 
 